### DeleteInstance - 删除实例 (HTTP)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/v1/instances/123456

### DeleteInstance - 删除实例 (gRPC)
GRPC localhost:9000/resource.v1.resourceService/DeleteInstance

{
  "instance_id": 123456
}

### StopInstance - 停止实例 (HTTP)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/instances/123456/stop
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instance_id": 123456
}

### StopInstance - 停止实例 (gRPC)
GRPC localhost:9000/resource.v1.resourceService/StopInstance

{
  "instance_id": 123456
}


### StartInstance - 启动实例 (HTTP)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/instances/123456/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instance_id": 123456
}

### StartInstance - 启动实例 (gRPC)
GRPC localhost:9000/resource.v1.resourceService/StartInstance

{
  "instance_id": 123456
}


### UpdateInstance - 更新实例规格 (HTTP)
PUT http://localhost:8000/v1/instances/123456
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instance_id": 123456,
  "cpu": 2,
  "memory": 2048,
  "gpu": 0,
  "image": "nginx:latest"
}

### UpdateInstance - 更新实例规格 (gRPC)
GRPC localhost:9000/resource.v1.resourceService/UpdateInstance

{
  "instance_id": 123456,
  "cpu": 2,
  "memory": 2048,
  "gpu": 0,
  "image": "nginx:latest"
}
